        {
            "type": "title",
            "content": {
                "title_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Pathloss Version 4.0 File Association "
                    }
                ],
                "level": 1
            },
            "bbox": [
                285,
                90,
                712,
                112
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "The pathloss installation program did not complete the Windows registry entry correctly on shipments before August 1999. Double clicking on a pathloss file (pl4) would start the program but did not load the file. The procedure to edit the registry and correct this problem is given in the steps below. "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                109,
                148,
                874,
                220
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "list",
            "content": {
                "list_type": "text_list",
                "list_items": [
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "Click Start - Run and enter the command line REGEDIT. Click OK to start the windows registry editor program. "
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "Select Edit - Find.. on the menu bar and enter the search string pl4file. "
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                111,
                238,
                872,
                347
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/ab795687ea2189f2a3ec38d59988454bff34feaa072cd225ba69ce5aa24659b8.jpg"
                },
                "content": "Find\nFind what: pl4file\nLook at\nKeys\nValues\nData\nMatch whole string only\nFind Next\nCancel",
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "sub_type": "text_image",
            "bbox": [
                372,
                290,
                887,
                470
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "The correct location is shown in the directory structure on the right. "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                111,
                472,
                509,
                508
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/2e29a2fb142ab0d47113cc59d514a3c4e7b0d80a9a0446ad71355997ac76565d.jpg"
                },
                "content": "pl4file\nDefaultIcon\nShell\nOpen\ncommand\nC:\\PLW40\\plw40.exe %1",
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "sub_type": "text_image",
            "bbox": [
                544,
                477,
                870,
                589
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "list",
            "content": {
                "list_type": "text_list",
                "list_items": [
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "Double click on the “ab” icon and edit the entry as shown. The %1 is the missing portion. The path name will be the directory that the pathloss program was installed in. "
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "Click OK and close REGEDIT program. "
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                112,
                598,
                388,
                780
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "image",
            "content": {
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/f5570cfad4440b36e377a399afa3dc6566fb837d4a848931c97355bb7489ce2e.jpg"
                },
                "content": "Edit String\nValue name:\n(Default)\nValue data:\nC:\\PLW40\\plw40.exe %1\nOK\tCancel",
                "image_caption": [],
                "image_footnote": []
            },
            "sub_type": "text_image",
